Lewis Hamilton taking his brother Nicolas in LA .
The two-time Formula One world champion took time out from training ahead of the Spanish Grand Prix next week to go cruising with his younger sibling in his stylish Shelby Cobra .
The 23-year-old younger half-brother of Lewis , suffers from the neurological condition cerebral palsy .
The Hamilton brothers will become the first driver with a disability to compete in the British Touring Championship in June .